<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= user.username %>'s Profile</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            background-color: #24ab3a;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-image: url('/images/profback.png'); /* Replace 'background.jpg' with your image file name */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); /* Overlay color with opacity */
            background-blend-mode: overlay;
        }

        .profile-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 40px;
            border: 1px solid #333333;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: #4c2b08;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .profile-left, .profile-right {
            flex: 1 1 45%;
            margin: 10px;
        }

        .profile-image {
            border-radius: 60%;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            border: 5px solid #ffffff;
            margin: 8px 40px 20px;
        }

        .profile-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }


        .profile-left p {
            writing-mode: vertical-rl;
            text-orientation: upright;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #cccccc;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .profile-right p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #bbbbbb;
        }

        .learn-more-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-left: 40px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 1px solid #ffffff;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .learn-more-btn:hover {
            background-color: #f9e2ca;
            color: #4c2b08;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="profile-container">
        <!-- Left Section -->
        <div class="profile-left">
            <div class="profile-image">
                <img src="<%= user.imageUrl %>" alt="<%= user.username %>">
            </div>
            <p></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Section -->
        <div class="profile-right">
            <h1>Ready to tell your love story?</h1>
            <p>
                <% if (quizData) { %>
                    <p>
                        Hey, I’m <strong><%= user.username %></strong> ! A <strong><%= quizData.hobby || 'hobby or interest' %></strong> enthusiast with a dream of travelling to <strong><%= quizData.dream || 'destination' %></strong> and that’s just wild enough to keep life interesting. My <strong><%= quizData.pet || 'pet' %></strong> is my partner-in-crime, and together, we’ve perfected the art of <strong><%= quizData.activity || 'activity' %></strong>. I live by the motto: <strong><%= quizData.philosophy || 'philosophy' %></strong>—because why not? I’m looking for someone with <strong><%= quizData.energy || 'energy' %></strong> vibes who’s ready to turn ordinary moments into unforgettable adventures. If that’s you, let’s see where this journey takes us!
                    </p>
                <% } else { %>
                    <p>Hi, I'm <strong><%= user.username %></strong>. I’m passionate about food, culture, and meaningful connections. 
                        I believe in creating memories through shared experiences. Let’s explore the world of <strong> <%= user.cuisine %></strong> together!</p>
                <% } %>
            </p>
            <a class="learn-more-btn" href="/restaurants?selectedUserId=<%= user.id %>">Accept</a>
            <a class="learn-more-btn" href="/suggested-users">Reject</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
